# Quick Look plugins
cask "glance-chamburr" # All-in-one Quick Look plugin: source code, Markdown, JSON, YAML, WebP, archives, Jupyter, and more. Modern .appex format. [Glance](https://github.com/chamburr/glance)
cask "qlvideo" # Quick Look plugin for video files. [QLVideo](https://github.com/Marginal/QLVideo)
